    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1OffscreenWindow" kindref="compound">OffscreenWindow</ref> provides a window-like interface for offscreen rendering. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>IMPORTANT: This is NOT a real native window! <ref refid="classDali_1_1OffscreenWindow" kindref="compound">OffscreenWindow</ref> is a rendering surface that uses framebuffer objects (FBO) to render UI content offscreen without creating an actual visible window on the screen.</para>
<para>IMPORTANT: You must call <ref refid="classDali_1_1OffscreenWindow_1a32ba7715847618f9e46ef32f87d5183b" kindref="member">SetNativeImage()</ref> to set the render target BEFORE calling <ref refid="classDali_1_1OffscreenApplication_1aa4b59970df115dd890ab3e95a1affda1" kindref="member">OffscreenApplication::Start()</ref>. The native image determines where the rendered content will be stored.</para>
<para>Usage Example: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>window<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classDali_1_1OffscreenWindow_1a04e5da3c7f4640efa591c79949d7af71" kindref="member">OffscreenWindow</ref>.New();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">window.SetBackgroundColor(Color::WHITE);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>IMPORTANT:<sp/>Set<sp/>native<sp/>image<sp/>BEFORE<sp/>starting<sp/>the<sp/>application</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="group__dali__adaptor__framework_1ga66ad744612018f55ae9bf88bc933e0e7" kindref="member">NativeImagePtr</ref><sp/>nativeImage<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classDali_1_1NativeImage_1a119603eb51a9705c8fbf57747c7bb450" kindref="member">NativeImage::New</ref>(width,<sp/>height);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">window.SetNativeImage(nativeImage);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Now<sp/>start<sp/>the<sp/>application</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">app.Start();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>UI<sp/>elements</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Actor<sp/>actor<sp/>=<sp/>Actor::New();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">window.Add(actor);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
